ActAppropriation Act No. 3, 2012-13
PrecisAppointment of DAVID ANGELL as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Uganda and High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Rwanda, with residence in Nairobi; GEORGES BOISSÉ as Ambassador of Canada to the Dominican Republic; ALEXANDRA BUGAILISKIS as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Poland; ANDRÉ DUBOIS as Ambassador of Canada to the State of Qatar; HEATHER GRANT as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Singapore; LOUISE LaROCQUE as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Croatia and as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Kosovo, with residence in Zagreb; SANDRA McCARDELL as Ambassador of Canada to the Kingdom of Morocco; ROBERT READY as High Commissioner for Canada to Jamaica, as Commissioner for Canada to the British Territories of the Cayman Islands, and as Commissioner for Canada to the British Territories of the Turks and Caicos Islands, with residence in Kingston; DAVID USHER as Ambassador of Canada to the Federal Democratic Republic of Ethiopia and Permanent Observer of Canada to the African Union in Addis Ababa and as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Djibouti, with residence in Addis Ababa; STEWART WHEELER as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Iceland; and SHELLEY WHITING as High Commissioner for Canada to the Democratic Socialist Republic of Sri Lanka and as High Commissioner for Canada to the Republic of Maldives, with residence in Colombo.
